                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 menu-course">
                  <div class="service-box-2">
                    <h3>2nd Course</h3>
                    <h4>Pan Seared Salmon </h4>
                    <h5>Pesto and Feta Bowtie Pasta Salad, Eggplant Caponata </h5>
                    <p>Paired with:</p>
                    <h4>Nia Pinot Noir, Mendocino County, CA </h4>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12">
                <div class="hr hr-png-6"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row col-md-12">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 menu-course">
                  <div class="service-box-2">
                    <h3>3rd Course</h3>
                    <h4>Veal Ossobucco Anglioti </h4>
                    <h5>Caramelized Onion and Roasted Tomatoes, Sprinkled with Gorgonzola Buerre Rouge </h5>
